Class SimpleDescribedEntity

java.lang.Object
org.uma.jmetal.util.naming.impl.SimpleDescribedEntity

Direct Known Subclasses:

public class SimpleDescribedEntity extends Object implements DescribedEntity
SimpleDescribedEntity is a basic implementation of DescribedEntity. It provides a basic support for the most generic properties required by this interface.
